name: Here Comes the Sun
description:
Limited Edition Print - this is from an original painting and is one of a limited edition of 80 signed and numbered by the artist. Each one is printed professionally using high-quality permanent pigments on premium pH-neutral 310gsm Hahnemühle fine art paper.

Your print will be sent in a sturdy cardboard tube. Payment is through Paypal and postage and packaging costs will be calculated in the shopping cart. Please see 'Postage & Packaging' in the right-hand column for details.
